                     <interp inst="t18481127-155-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp> for stealing 5 spoons, 5 forks, and 1 basket, value 10<hi rend="italic">l</hi>.; the property of <persName id="t18481127-name-807" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18481127-name-807" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
